{"tid":2146744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TikTok據報擬入稟挑戰特朗普的行政命令","createTime":"2020-08-08T19:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T00:08:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"26ec831d133cc40ce805ebb31bd4b86b5e09b0e5","tid":2146744,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:28:12.000Z","msg":"美國傳媒報道，中國影片分享程式「抖音國際版」TikTok，計劃就美國總統特朗普，禁止美國企業與TikTok母公司「字節跳動」交易，提出訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家公共電台引述消息人士說，TikTok最快會在當地星期二，入稟公司美國總部所在的南加州聯邦法院，挑戰特朗普的行政命令。消息人士說，TikTok認為特朗普的行動違憲，因為它並無給予公司回應的機會，又認為華府在這項行政命令中援引的國家安全理由，是毫無根據。<br />\n<br />\n白宮拒絕就可能出現的訴訟發表評論，但就為特朗普的行政命令辯護，強調政府致力保障美國人民，免受所有與網絡相關的威脅。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542651-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542651-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiWzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=eac7badc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542651-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=71bd511b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542651-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4945a53ba04e2c957489e0b37e15bdf446d38aec","tid":2146744,"uid":21545,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"美國：國安大於一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6616ab5b6ea26807dd12c9aed899049dfd65e28b","tid":2146744,"uid":88743,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"咁唔鐘意特朗普<br />\nquit美國囉"},{"pid":"09b0ef9ff0e27942eda61d2d6449daf9704afc79","tid":2146744,"uid":284699,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:35:01.000Z","msg":"之前試過用國家安全封你企業啦，全部政府勝訴"},{"pid":"ef0af12a94bcfb13235aa11731e7b3867a132c12","tid":2146744,"uid":42364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTim